question: How many flights were operated by each aircraft model in Q2 2024?
query:
SELECT a.model,
       COUNT(*) AS flight_count
FROM postgres_air.flight f
JOIN postgres_air.aircraft a ON f.aircraft_code = a.code
WHERE f.scheduled_departure >= '2024-04-01' AND f.scheduled_departure < '2024-07-01'
GROUP BY a.model;
